{
  "texts": [
    "Two groups were established in this study: a control group, utilizing GPT-4 for direct question answering, and an experimental group (RAG-GPT), employing a BGE-embedding RAG model 17 for embedding, which performed semantic matching retrieval on the input questions.",
    "The retrieved local knowledge was integrated into the input question before being sent to the GPT-4 system (Fig. 1).",
    "The platform was based on Windows 11, with a computer equipped with an Intel Core i9 CPU, 64 GB of flash memory, an NVIDIA 3090 GPU, a 4 TB mechanical hard drive, and a 512 GB solid-state drive.",
    "The software was programmed in Python 3.11, and the base model was assessed using the GPT-4 API provided by OpenAI.",
    "The RAG model was run using CUDA 11.8, in conjunction with a GPU."
  ]
}